## Domain sections

> Add new `## <Domain>` headings + stable-anchor entries for every
> scar this project earns. Template per entry:

```markdown
<a id="anchor-name"></a>
### §ANCHOR-NAME — one-line summary

**Symptom.** What the user/agent observes.

**Root cause.** Why it happens.

**Do NOT.** Anti-patterns to avoid.

**Do.** Correct pattern with code or steps.

**Where.** `path/to/file.ext::function_name`

**Shipped in.** `<commit sha>`.
```

Add the anchor to the Table of Contents above too, under the
appropriate category. Use `atlas anchor add NAME "summary"` to
scaffold a stub.

